source.name: Gas Stations in Washington DC
source.description: Gas Station locations. The dataset contains locations and attributes of Gas Stations, created as part of the DC Geographic Information System (DC GIS) for the D.C. Office of the Chief Technology Officer (OCTO) and participating D.C. government agencies.
